{"type":"message","id":"275721a3","parentId":"75cf483b","timestamp":"2026-05-07T09:17:31.845Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我了解了技能结构。让我开始实施升级：\n\n1. P0: SSH专项增强\n   - 创建SSH专项规则文件（增强现有SSH规则）\n   - 创建SSH自动修复脚本\n\n2. P1: 文档细化\n   - 创建SSH修复详细指南\n   - 更新规则文件添加修复建议\n   - 更新FAQ增加SSH专题\n\n3. P2: 批量检查功能\n   - 创建批量扫描脚本\n\n让我开始实施这些功能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在开始全面升级！创建SSH专项增强功能："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:38","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/rules/ssh-004.yaml","content":"id: ssh-004\nname: SSH Root Login Disabled\ndescription: |\n  检查SSH是否禁用root用户直接登录\n  \n  安全风险:\n  - root用户直接登录一旦密码泄露，攻击者获得最高权限\n  - 无法进行用户操作审计\n  \n  修复建议:\n  1. 编辑 /etc/ssh/sshd_config\n  2. 设置 PermitRootLogin no\n  3. 重启SSH服务: systemctl restart sshd\ncategory: security\nseverity: high\ncheck_type: config\nconfig_path: /etc/ssh/sshd_config\npattern: \"^PermitRootLogin\\\\s+no\"\nexpect_match: true\nfix_command: |\n  sudo sed -i 's/^#*PermitRootLogin.*/PermitRootLogin no/' /etc/ssh/sshd_config &&\n  sudo systemctl restart sshd\nfix_description: \"禁用root登录并重启SSH服务\"\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:39","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/rules/ssh-005.yaml","content":"id: ssh-005\nname: SSH Key Authentication Only\ndescription: |\n  检查SSH是否强制使用密钥认证（禁用密码认证）\n  \n  安全风险:\n  - 密码认证容易被暴力破解\n  - 密钥认证提供更强的安全性\n  \n  修复建议:\n  1. 编辑 /etc/ssh/sshd_config\n  2. 设置 PasswordAuthentication no\n  3. 设置 PubkeyAuthentication yes\n  4. 重启SSH服务\n  \n  ⚠️ 警告: 启用前确保已配置SSH密钥，否则会被锁定！\ncategory: security\nseverity: high\ncheck_type: config\nconfig_path: /etc/ssh/sshd_config\npattern: \"^PasswordAuthentication\\\\s+no\"\nexpect_match: true\nfix_command: |\n  echo \"⚠️  警告: 启用密钥认证前请确保已配置SSH密钥！\" &&\n  read -p \"确认已配置密钥并继续? (yes/no): \" confirm &&\n  [ \"$confirm\" = \"yes\" ] &&\n  sudo sed -i 's/^#*PasswordAuthentication.*/PasswordAuthentication no/' /etc/ssh/sshd_config &&\n  sudo sed -i 's/^#*PubkeyAuthentication.*/PubkeyAuthentication yes/' /etc/ssh/sshd_config &&\n  sudo systemctl restart sshd\nfix_description: \"禁用密码认证，仅允许密钥认证\"\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:40","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/rules/ssh-006.yaml","content":"id: ssh-006\nname: SSH Protocol Version 2\ndescription: |\n  检查SSH是否使用安全的协议版本2\n  \n  安全风险:\n  - SSH协议版本1存在严重安全漏洞\n  - 版本2提供更强大的加密和认证机制\n  \n  修复建议:\n  1. 编辑 /etc/ssh/sshd_config\n  2. 添加或修改 Protocol 2\n  3. 重启SSH服务\ncategory: security\nseverity: medium\ncheck_type: config\nconfig_path: /etc/ssh/sshd_config\npattern: \"^Protocol\\\\s+2\"\nexpect_match: true\nfix_command: |\n  sudo sed -i 's/^#*Protocol.*/Protocol 2/' /etc/ssh/sshd_config &&\n  sudo systemctl restart sshd\nfix_description: \"强制使用SSH协议版本2\"\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:41","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/rules/ssh-007.yaml","content":"id: ssh-007\nname: SSH Port Changed from Default\ndescription: |\n  检查SSH是否使用非默认端口（22以外的端口）\n  \n  安全优势:\n  - 减少自动化攻击扫描\n  - 降低被暴力破解的概率\n  \n  修复建议:\n  1. 编辑 /etc/ssh/sshd_config\n  2. 修改 Port 2222（或其他高位端口）\n  3. 重启SSH服务\n  4. 更新防火墙规则\n  \n  ⚠️ 注意: 修改后需要使用新端口连接！\ncategory: security\nseverity: medium\ncheck_type: config\nconfig_path: /etc/ssh/sshd_config\npattern: \"^Port\\\\s+(?!22\\\\s*$)\\\\d+\"\nexpect_match: true\nfix_command: |\n  read -p \"请输入新SSH端口(1024-65535): \" port &&\n  [ \"$port\" -ge 1024 ] && [ \"$port\" -le 65535 ] &&\n  sudo sed -i \"s/^#*Port.*/Port $port/\" /etc/ssh/sshd_config &&\n  sudo systemctl restart sshd &&\n  echo \"SSH端口已修改为 $port，请使用新端口连接！\"\nfix_description: \"修改SSH默认端口\"\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":1210,"output":1282,"cacheRead":75776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78268,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778145417098,"responseId":"chatcmpl-69fc5889944cbca1be943433"}}
