{"type":"message","id":"7cbaea5f","parentId":"93b7770d","timestamp":"2026-05-07T09:22:34.875Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:58","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 6. SSH修复脚本功能测试 ===\n\n========================================\n       SSH安全配置检查报告\n========================================\n\n检查项                                状态\n----------------------------------------\n1. 禁用root登录 (PermitRootLogin no) ✗ (当前: PermitRootLogin yes)\n2. 禁用密码认证 (PasswordAuthentication no) ✗ (当前: PasswordAuthentication yes)\n3. 启用密钥认证 (PubkeyAuthentication yes) ✓\n4. 使用SSH协议版本2 (Protocol 2)   ✗ (当前: '未设置')\n5. 修改默认端口 (Port ≠ 22)      ✗ (当前使用默认端口22)\n----------------------------------------"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":25,"aggregated":"=== 6. SSH修复脚本功能测试 ===\n\n========================================\n       SSH安全配置检查报告\n========================================\n\n检查项                                状态\n----------------------------------------\n1. 禁用root登录 (PermitRootLogin no) ✗ (当前: PermitRootLogin yes)\n2. 禁用密码认证 (PasswordAuthentication no) ✗ (当前: PasswordAuthentication yes)\n3. 启用密钥认证 (PubkeyAuthentication yes) ✓\n4. 使用SSH协议版本2 (Protocol 2)   ✗ (当前: '未设置')\n5. 修改默认端口 (Port ≠ 22)      ✗ (当前使用默认端口22)\n----------------------------------------","cwd":"/workspace/projects/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778145754875}}
