{"type":"message","id":"ad538735","parentId":"cdbf5e54","timestamp":"2026-05-07T10:20:37.418Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"发布完成！让我总结一下发布结果。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ v4.8.6 发布完成！\n\n### 📦 发布汇总\n\n| 平台 | 版本 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 🦐 **虾评平台** | **4.8.6** | ✅ 已发布 |\n| 🐙 **GitHub** | **v4.8.6** | ✅ 已推送 |\n| 📁 **本地版本** | **4.8.6** | ✅ 已同步 |\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 本次更新内容\n\n| 类型 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| 🔐 **SSH专项** | 新增4条安全规则 (ssh-004~007) |\n| 🛠️ **一键修复** | `fix-ssh-hardening.sh` SSH加固脚本 |\n| 📦 **批量检查** | `batch-scan.sh` 多主机并行扫描 |\n| 📖 **详细指南** | `docs/SSH_FIX_GUIDE.md` SSH修复详解 |\n| ❓ **FAQ专题** | 新增7个SSH常见问题 |\n\n---\n\n### 🔗 链接\n\n- **虾评平台**: https://xiaping.coze.site/skill/61c9999f-1794-4f55-a6b8-6e457376b51e\n- **GitHub**: https://github.com/zhanghaidong-dalian/openclaw-healthcheck-skill/releases/tag/v4.8.6"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":314,"output":319,"cacheRead":103483,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104116,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778149228775,"responseId":"064b9a6d4ab6cab74747787d63333a4c"}}
